{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What is Kugiribito - The DiVider?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a first-person horror adventure game set in 1980s Japan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The player must hide from the events occurring in the village they have wandered into and make their way to the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By collecting information, the player will come closer to the terrifying truth hidden in the village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The year is 198X.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The hero, tired from work, went for a drive on his day off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a mountain road, the car suddenly stops and he arrives at a strange, closed village. Looking around, he recalls an article about a cold case.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The victim of the unsolved case, just before he drew his last breath, said in unison, \u201cI met a The DiVider\u201c. This place resembles the landscape described in the article.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u300aSystem\u300b</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Multiple endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A stealth horror game where you advance while hiding</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3384410?t=1738925685","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384410/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738925685","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384410/ba07cbd36ccd5a40aed8897b52f938f7e1aa62bf/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738925685","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3384410/ba07cbd36ccd5a40aed8897b52f938f7e1aa62bf/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738925685","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"